\n                font-size: 2.5rem;\n            }\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            section h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8rem;\n            }\n            .portfolio-grid {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Elara Vance</h1>\n        <p>Illustrator & Graphic Novelist</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About Me</h2>\n            <p>\n                Elara Vance is a passionate graphic novelist and illustrator who weaves intricate worlds and compelling characters through her art. With a deep love for storytelling and a unique visual style, Elara brings her narratives to life with a rich palette and dynamic compositions. Her work often explores themes of fantasy, mystery, and the human condition, rendered in a signature indigo-infused aesthetic.\n            </p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"portfolio\">\n            <h2>Selected Works</h2>\n            <div class=\"portfolio-grid\">\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/4B0082/ffffff?text=The+Crimson+Tear\" alt=\"The Crimson Tear Cover\">\n                    <div class=\"portfolio-item-info\">\n                        <h3>The Crimson Tear</h3>\n                        <p>A dark fantasy epic filled with ancient magic and a quest for redemption.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/734f9c/ffffff?text=Whispers+in+the+Nebula\" alt=\"Whispers in the Nebula Cover\">\n                    <div class=\"portfolio-item-info\">\n                        <h3>Whispers in the Nebula</h3>\n                        <p>A sci-fi mystery exploring a lost colony ship and its secrets.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/4B0082/ffffff?text=The+Clockwork+Heart\" alt=\"The Clockwork Heart Cover\">\n                    <div class=\"portfolio-item-info\">\n                        <h3>The Clockwork Heart</h3>\n                        <p>A steampunk adventure with intricate machinery and a battle against time.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x250/734f9c/ffffff?text=Midnight+Grove\" alt=\"Midnight Grove Cover\">\n                    <div class=\"portfolio-item-info\">\n                        <h3>Midnight Grove</h3>\n                        <p>A coming-of-age story set in a magical forest, exploring friendship and courage.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n                Interested in collaboration or commissions? Feel free to reach out!\n            </p>\n            <div class=\"social-links\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;\">\n                <a href=\"mailto:elara.vance.art@email.com\" aria-label=\"Email Elara Vance\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-envelope\"></i> <!-- Placeholder for icon, requires Font Awesome -->\n                </a>\n                <a href=\"https://www.twitter.com/elara_vance_art\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"Twitter\">\n                    <i class=\"fab fa-twitter\"></i> <!-- Placeholder for icon -->\n                </a>\n                <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/elara_vance_art\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"Instagram\">\n                    <i class=\"fab fa-instagram\"></i> <!-- Placeholder for icon -->\n                </a>\n            </div>\n        